Interface SearchFilter<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the object to check.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SongSearchFilter
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface SearchFilter<T>
    Represents a generic filter that evaluate a predicate against an instance of a given type.
